peopleAlsoAsk.question: Are vintage beer cans worth anything?
peopleAlsoAsk.snippet: Lightweight aluminum cans, in most cases, will have little or no value. Any flat top, zip tab, fan tab or juice tab cans will have some value. Also, just about any cone top, quart cone top or crowntainer will be valuable, except for a couple of notable fakes like Milwaukee and General Pulaski cone tops.
